TAGLIST_DESCRIPTION: Views the players current tags and lock/unlock status
NO_TAGS_SELF: {{author}} You don't have any tags yet. Use the command `{{prefix}}tc <TagName> <Emoji>` to create one
NO_TAGS: {{author}} That user does not have any tags
SOFI_FACT: A locked tag cannot be burnt or traded
TAGLIST_EXTRA_INFO: Views the players current tags and lock/unlock status. Using this command without a prompt will show your tag list, adding another player's username or user id will show their tag list. Lock card or version tags cannot be burned, trade or gave away. You can use the "{{prefix}}tagcreate" command in order to create more card or version tags
